text: The flag of Tonalá () It is colored white and the coat of arms in the center. The emblem has a diameter of three-quarters the width of the stripes. The ratio of the flag is 4:7. ==Related pages== * Tonalá ==References== Tonalá Category:Tonalá Tonalá Category:Flags with coats of arms
